item.title: Help me!
item.dc:creator: @mage_burst mage_burst
item.description:
@mage_burst wrote:

You have to have ur server source compiled and running while u get on ur server, you enter a random username and password u will remeber and click enter, if this makes it eaiser ill make a list of what to do,
[ul][li]1.Open ur server source.[/li]
[li]2.Click compile.[list][list]
[li]3.Click Run server.[/li]
[li]4.Leave the window up where it says ur source is running.[/li]
[/list][list]
[li]5.Open Moparscape.[/li]
[li]Enter a username and password u will remeber.[/li]
[/list][list]
[li]6.Last but not least click enter u should log into ur server.[/li]
[/list]
I hope this helped.
[/list][/ul]
